### RAG Semantic Search (Vector Search)
# Pure semantic similarity search using embedding vectors and cosine similarity.
# Best for: Conceptual similarity, natural language queries, finding documents with similar meaning but different wording.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@apiKey = your-api-key

### Basic Semantic Search
# Simple vector similarity search without additional filters
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/semantic
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query_embedding": [0.023, -0.045, 0.128, 0.003, -0.087],
  "top_k": 10
}

### Semantic Search with Filters
# Search with minimum similarity threshold and job_id filter
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/semantic
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query_embedding": [0.023, -0.045, 0.128, 0.003, -0.087],
  "top_k": 10,
  "min_similarity": 0.75,
  "filters": {
    "job_id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
  }
}

###
